$ITEMSEP
$ITEM Find a basis for \( \mathrm{span}(\mathcal{C}) \).
Enter a polynomial or a comma separated list of polynomials.
$BR
\( \big\lbrace \) \{ ans_rule(50) \} \( \big\rbrace \)

$ITEMSEP
